Class ReaderParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.CoreObject
      • org.apache.juneau.parser.Parser
        • org.apache.juneau.parser.ReaderParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CsvParser, JsonParser, PlainTextParser, RdfParser, UonParser, XmlParser

    public abstract class ReaderParser
extends Parser
    Subclass of Parser for characters-based parsers.
    Description:

    This class is typically the parent class of all character-based parsers. It has 1 abstract method to implement...

    • parse(ParserSession, ClassMeta)
    @Consumes annotation

    The media types that this parser can handle is specified through the @Consumes annotation.

    However, the media types can also be specified programmatically by overriding the Parser.getMediaTypes() method.
